a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6110379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6110379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xrd1707815497645.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xrd1707815497645.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xrd1707815497645.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"efp1665702543889\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Assignments\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">In ProcScript, the equal sign (<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>) assigns the result of an expression to a variable, parameter, field, or status function.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14510e1_d14511e1_d14512e1\">The general format of a ProcScript assignment is:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14513e1_d14514e1_d14515e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14516e1_d14517e1_d14518e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14519e1_d14520e1_d14521e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">@</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14522e1_d14523e1_d14524e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Function</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14525e1_d14526e1_d14527e1\">where:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"efp1665702543889__li_d7046e1_d7047e1_d7048e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>—specifies the literal name of a local varaible, component variable or global variable\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"efp1665702543889__li_d7049e1_d7050e1_d7051e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>—specifies the literal name of a field to which <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is assigned\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"efp1665702543889__li_d7052e1_d7053e1_d7054e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">@</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>—specifies the literal name of a field that holds the name of the field to which <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is assigned\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"efp1665702543889__li_d7055e1_d7056e1_d7057e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Function</var>—specifies the literal name of a status function to which <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is assigned\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"efp1665702543889__li_d7058e1_d7059e1_d7060e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>—specifies the expression that is being used to generate a value.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14528e1_d14529e1_d14530e1\">An expression can always be assigned to, or substituted in, a string. Uniface performs implicit data type conversion if the expression is of a data type other then String.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"efp1665702543889__section_xkz_j2p_k1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885714e166\">Example: Assignments in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14534e1_d14535e1_d14536e1\">The following ProcScript example shows a basic\n            assignment:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"efp1665702543889__pre_f43_l2p_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">myVar = \"My expression\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14537e1_d14538e1_d14539e1\">The following ProcScript example shows an assignment\n            in combination with a ProcScript function:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"efp1665702543889__pre_g43_l2p_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = $lowercase(\"My expression\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"efp1665702543889__p_d14540e1_d14541e1_d14542e1\">The following ProcScript example shows an assignment\n            to an indirected field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"efp1665702543889__pre_h43_l2p_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">FIELD1 = \"\"\nFIELDNAME = \"FIELD1\"\n@FIELDNAME = $lowercase(\"My expression\")\n; Result: FIELD1 contains \"my expression\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/etu1719376772254.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>= (compute)</a><p>Assigns the value of an expression to a field, variable, or function.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6110379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6110379\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Assignments Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Assignments In ProcScript, the equal sign ( = ) assigns the result of an expression to a variable, parameter, field, or status function. The general format of a ProcScript assignment is: Variable = Expression Field = Expression @ Field = Expression $ Function = Expression where: Variable —specifies the literal name of a local varaible, component variable or global variable Field —specifies the literal name of a field to which Expression is assigned @ Field —specifies the literal name of a field that holds the name of the field to which Expression is assigned $ Function —specifies the literal name of a status function to which Expression is assigned Expression —specifies the expression that is being used to generate a value. An expression can always be assigned to, or substituted in, a string. Uniface performs implicit data type conversion if the expression is of a data type other then String. Example: Assignments in ProcScript The following ProcScript example shows a basic assignment: myVar = \"My expression\" Copy The following ProcScript example shows an assignment in combination with a ProcScript function: $1 = $lowercase(\"My expression\") Copy The following ProcScript example shows an assignment to an indirected field: FIELD1 = \"\" FIELDNAME = \"FIELD1\" @FIELDNAME = $lowercase(\"My expression\") ; Result: FIELD1 contains \"my expression\" Copy Related Links = (compute) Assigns the value of an expression to a field, variable, or function. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}